<P>
 The men's and women's cross-country teams from Mt. SAC and PCC and the women's 
team from Citrus College qualified for the state championships in Fresno with 
their performances last weekend at the Johnie O Invitational at Moorpark 
College. 
</P>
<P>
 The Mt. SAC men's team finished second behind Riverside. Mt. SAC sophomore 
Luis Baca and freshman Warren Wolf both covered the four-mile course in 21 
minutes, 4 seconds to finish eighth and ninth, respectively. 
