Saturday and Sunday at the grand opening of the All-American In-Line Hockey 
League in Northridge. Skating exhibitions and a charity sports memorabilia 
auction also are scheduled. 
</P>
<P>
 Registration will be held for youth and adult teams at the outdoor facility, 
18000 Devonshire St.  
</P>
