<P>
 Notre Dame High girls' basketball player Maggie Dixon said Wednesday night she 
will play for the University of San Diego. 
</P>
<P>
 Dixon, a 6-foot-1 senior, averaged 11.7 points and 10.3 rebounds a game last 
season for the Knights. 
