<TEXT>
<P>
 Michelle Weisz of El Dorado defeated teammate Linda Surapruik in the singles 
final, 6-2, 6-1, on Wednesday in Orange League girls' tennis finals. 
</P>
<P>
 In the semifinals, Surapruik and Weisz upset Katella's Nos. 1 and 2 singles, 
