semifinals. All four of the top seeded players advanced. 
</P>
<P>
 In the Sunset League: 
</P>
<P>
 Arvizu and Rosenthal advance -- Top-seeded Allison Arvizu of Huntington Beach 
and Los Alamitos' Melissa Rosenthal, second-seeded, advanced to the semifinals 
of the Sunset League.  
</P>
<P>
 Arvizu won, 6-1, 6-1, and Rosenthal went, 6-2, 6-0, in the quarterfinal round. 
In the quarterfinal doubles, Alison Miller and Michelle Schneider of Los 
Alamitos and El Dorado's Tami Demaree and Susie Krum, also advanced.  
</P>
