<DOCNO> LA110394-0335 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 095036 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
November 3, 1994, Thursday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 1; Column 6; Metro Desk 
</P>
