Middle School in Canoga Park: Nearly 75 students marched around campus; most 
returned. Taft High School in Woodland Hills: About 600 students left campus; 
most returned. 
</P>
<P>
 Van Nuys High School: At least 100 students left classes; most returned on 
school buses; Van Nuys Middle School: About 40 students left campus; some 
returned. 
